:"429189f46a4dcc3bcd5682dcd4ead855561a5c1d","tid":1209541,"uid":88263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"石禮謙話畀大家知，香港人最緊張嘅係經濟<br />\n<br />\n講個知識畀大家知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每塞6分鐘車，就會有28億損失</span></span><br />\n<br />\n舊Source： <a href=\"https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2F%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=c1e2b411\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.master-insight.com/塞車造成多少經濟損失？/</a><br />\n<br />\n重鐵同時間載到40幾萬人，繁忙時間以每平方米4個人計嘅運載量到9成<br />\n<br />\n只要帶手提行李就會每平方米大約企到2個人，即係20幾萬人會打爆重鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">舉個例子</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">100萬人遊行散場，要現有運載力嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5倍</span>先可以運走啲人</span></span>，但留意返香港有7百幾萬人，又有遊客。一百萬人散場，實際所需運載力係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大過5倍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家請守法體驗一流港鐵服務<br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef2374b908ff02902b02d5f1af6afc1b3de3ddf1","tid":1209541,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"北大快速今日好多運狗車駐紮<br />\n青衣上橋<br />\n收費廣場<br />\n小蠔灣廠<br />\n東涌回旋<br />\n來回有馬巡<br />\n全部係新界南交通"},{"pid":"e267ae95b9154b595fca488d67ea7ecfc88581cd","tid":1209541,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"新界巴打支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班友搞事係度佔中做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一於遊車河 有無路線等我黎匯合"}]}